Books have always been the traditional way to learn from many years ago. However, nowadays, computers and tablets are emerging into the educational system and schools are starting to use them more.Computer tablets have both advantages and disadvantages. In the present paper I will discuss whether the use of computer tablets is the alternative tool for education or not.
Singer and Alexander (2016) found that school students enjoyed using tablets more than print textbooks but learned better when they used print textbooks. This finding suggests that tablets are better when it comes to enjoying the learning process, which is an essential factor.